parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can result in serious injury or death to the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard comes on
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the seatbelt fails to tighten or retract
the vehicle sustains significant damage in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag light illumination can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy in a crash, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard comes on
the airbag system malfunctions
the passenger airbag off light illuminates when an adult sits in the passenger seat and secures the seatbelt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring and circuitry can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to failure to deploy in a crash, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard comes on
the airbag system malfunctions
the clock spring and circuitry need to be repaired or replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate or fail to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate
the transmission shifts erratically
the vehicle surges or lunges forward
the transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The key becoming stuck in the ignition can cause the vehicle to be left unattended with the key in the ignition, making it vulnerable to theft.
symptoms: The key becomes stuck in the ignition
the key cannot be removed from the ignition
the key sticks in the ignition after shifting into park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to hesitate or fail to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position.
